import styles from './formContainer.module.css'

                    </div>

                    </div>

                    <div className={`${styles['input-container']}`}>

                    </div>

                    <div className={`${styles['input-container']}`}>

                            <option value="C">Current</option>
                            <option value="O">Other</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
